				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This drow was petrified by a spectator. And will still feel a bit sick when he's woken up. Disoriented somewhat.\r\nNow he is unpetrified.\r\nWorries about his companions and the group's leader - the wizard.\r\nLeave after a long rest."
